===============================================================================

PdfjsViewer has been installed successfully!

The configuration file has been created at:
  config/initializers/pdfjs_viewer.rb

You can customize the PDF.js viewer by editing this file to show/hide
various toolbar buttons and features.

To mount the PDF viewer in your application, add this to your routes.rb:

  mount PdfjsViewer::Engine => "/pdfjs"

Then you can access the viewer at:
  http://localhost:3000/pdfjs/viewer?file=path/to/your.pdf

For more information, visit: https://github.com/your-username/pdfjs_viewer

===============================================================================